</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Enjoying a last sunset in Redondo Beach. 夕日を眺める 夕日を眺める レドンドビーチで最後の夕日を満喫する。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09680-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09680-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Evening at Avenue I</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250919/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Evening at Avenue I" /><published>2025-09-19T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-09-19T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/avenue-i</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250919/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
