</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Lifeguard Towers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking across the Santa Monica Bay towards Malibu this evening, from the south end of Redondo Beach. A sailboat heads home to King Harbor Marina, while in the distance at right are the ever present El Segundo oil tankers. A couple enjoys the view. アベニューIの夕べ 今夕、レドンド・ビーチの南端からサンタモニカ湾をマリブ方面に眺める。ヨットがキング・ハーバー・マリーナに帰港し、右の遠方にはエルセグンドの石油タンカーが見える。景色を楽しむカップル。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09695_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2509_A7R09695_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hermosa Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250916/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hermosa Sunset" /><published>2025-09-16T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-09-16T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hermosa-sunset</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250916/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
